5 A BILL
6 TO BE ENTITLED
7 AN ACT
8
9 Relating to the Alabama Criminal Justice Information
10 Commission; to add Section 41-9-623.2 to the Code of Alabama
11 1975; to amend Section 41-9-600, Code of Alabama 1975; to
12 require each state, county, and municipal law enforcement
13 agency to report the number of sworn law enforcement officers
14 employed by the local law enforcement agency to the Alabama
15 Criminal Justice Information Commission; to revise penalties
16 for failure to submit reports to the commission; to require
17 the commission to share the information in certain reports
18 with the Alabama State Law Enforcement Agency and Attorney
19 General; and to authorize the agency to adopt rules.
20 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
21 Section 1. Section 41-9-623.2 is added to the Code of
22 Alabama 1975, to read as follows:
23 §41-9-623.2
24 (a) This section shall be known as the Sergeant WyTasha
25 Carter Truth and Transparency Act.
26 (b) Not later than July 1, 2026, and February 1,
27 annually thereafter, each criminal justice agency shall report
28 all of the following on a form prescribed by the Alabama State
Page 1

all of the following on a form prescribed by the Alabama State
