57 official shall also be subject to prosecution for nonfeasance
58 and, if found guilty, shall be subject to removal from office
59 therefor.
60 (c) Any criminal justice agency that fails to submit
61 any report required under this article shall lose the ability
62 to participate in any grant program administered by the
63 Alabama Department of Economic and Community Affairs until the
64 agency meets the conditions of compliance."
65 Section 3. This act shall become effective on June 1,
66 2026.
